code:
sequenceDiagram
    participant AlbumPage
    participant AlbumDAO
    participant ImageDAO
    participant CTX
    participant TemplateEngine

    AlbumPage ->>+ AlbumDAO: new AlbumDAO(Infra_RedisCache)
    AlbumPage ->> AlbumDAO: get(Infra_LoadBalancer)
    alt album exists
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional<Album>
        AlbumPage ->>+ ImageDAO: new ImageDAO(Infra_RedisCache)
        AlbumPage ->> ImageDAO: getAlbumImages(Infra_EtcdCluster)
        ImageDAO -->> AlbumPage: images
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Infra_IngressController)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Infra_RedisCache)
        AlbumPage -->> CTX: setVariable(Infra_EtcdCluster)
        AlbumPage -->> TemplateEngine: process(Infra_IngressController)
    else album does not exist
        AlbumDAO -->> AlbumPage: Optional.empty(Infra_EtcdCluster)
        AlbumPage --> AlbumPage: response.sendError(Infra_EtcdCluster)
    end
